===Etymology===
*[[pseudo-]] + [[science]]

===Noun===
'''pseudoscience'''
#Any body of [[knowledge]] purported to be scientific or supported by [[science]] but which fails to comply with the [[scientific method]].

===Usage note===
This term is often used by people who have no underlying familiarity with the subject under consideration, and is thus seen as pejorative many.  It's use should be avoided in the absence of relevant information.

